{"tid":1514734,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人食完催淚彈放題之後連教小朋友方法都進化左","createTime":"2019-08-29T00:51:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T01:51:52.000Z","uid":38451,"like":41,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6346c2dd526a06f355325c7cc944b8a3ad899dfd","tid":1514734,"uid":38451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T00:51:03.000Z","msg":"一個滿頭白髮既伯伯帶個孫上小巴<br />\n個孫想坐近門口位<br />\n伯伯好大聲咁講「坐入去啊，冇小朋友坐出面架，你曳曳警察拉你走，放催淚彈架，扔催淚彈去你到架！」<br />\n<br />\n警察係咪都放催淚彈呢個事實會名垂青史，一代傳一代，唔好忘記我地係食催淚彈大。<br />\n我聽到笑左，真人真事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b36b6242891fbafa718d4f9450e891fe7f49e0d5","tid":1514734,"uid":62811,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T00:53:31.000Z","msg":"我前日聽到樓下啲𡃁仔稱呼佢地要避嗰舊玩具叫催淚彈"},{"pid":"d4ad9567e421570e54f918eab66439810e17d6ba","tid":1514734,"uid":28921,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T01:01:11.000Z","msg":"起碼小學雞寫我的志願無乜人寫做狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd0ccda8907b94b56db57e453a4240182a3e184b","tid":1514734,"uid":250444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T01:04:46.000Z","msg":"屌 你哋係咪誤解左兄弟爬山嘅意思<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1514726\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1514726</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"86778a749ae124273d47e0669b9bad4d40961536","tid":1514734,"uid":213217,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d4ad9567e421570e54f918eab66439810e17d6ba","tid":1514734,"uid":28921,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T01:01:11.000Z","msg":"起碼小學雞寫我的志願無乜人寫做狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T01:05:51.000Z","msg":"我細個寫警察律師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3b344aba3dc45b3b88a2921fb35ef75cb9c05b0","tid":1514734,"uid":256975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T01:06:45.000Z",